<span id="freeTextContainer9363834043192522203">I was NOT a &quot;non-believer&quot; when I opened this book. I considered myself a believer in the spiritual realm, if not any organized religion. If I had label myself I&apos;d say I was agnostic. By the end of the book I was quite prepared to say that I am an atheist. <br/><br/>People make lists of the books that impacted their lives. This one is top of mine. For better or worse!</span>
