    <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/author/list/3956.Christopher_Hitchens">Books by Christopher Hitchens</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
